No.1/34/1/2019-Cab. (iii)
GOVERNMENT OF INDIA (BHARAT SARKAR)
CABINET SECRETARIAT (MANTRIMANDAL SACHIVALAYA)
To
The undersigned is directed to say that Shri Narendra Modi has been sworn in as the
Prime Minister by the President at 1900 hours, today, the 30th May 2019, in the Rashtrapati
Bhavan, New Delhi.
MOST IMMEDIATE
2.
The Ministers as shown in the list attached have also been sworn in by the President
at 1900 hours, today, the 30th May, 2019, in the Rashtrapati Bhawan, New Delhi.
All Members of the Council of Ministers.
Copy forwarded for information to:
Secretary to the President.
Secretary to the Vice-President.
Copy also forwarded for information to :
Principal Secretary to the Prime Minister.
Additional Principal Secretary to the Prime Minister.
New Delhi, the 30th May, 2019
Copy also forwarded for information to :
Secretary-General (Lok Sabha).
Secretary-General (Rajya Sabha).
